descriptionHtml:
Adds a Wilderness Shack on a new island in the lake of Ilinalta in the Falkreath Hold Territory. 
 To find the shack simply go north from Falkreath Hold until you reach the lake and take a swim =]
 The Shack comes complete with most of the crafting tools i.e Anvil, Smelter, Tanning Rack. 

 The Shack has no load screen as does not have its own cell, i thought it maybe cool to have an  open player home. Let me know what you think.
author: JMAG
